{
  "stem": "1918.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 261.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I came from a middle-class family and had a nice home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had a chamber maid and, and wet nurse for the children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All of this was-- you know, some people had a better life, but most of them were poor, I believe.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe it was a town of about 20,000.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were several thousand Jews, maybe 4,000.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It had to be 4,000 Jews rather than 4,000 families.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was a large Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a very-- I surely can recall a lot of Jewish life, an intelligent and motivated lifestyle where people studied and, and read and were interested in everything in the world, particularly in politics because somehow our lives always depended on the whims of the governments--",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--how anti-Semitic they were.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I come from a very Orthodox family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And though my father was one of those modern-looking Orthodox men, he was more Orthodox than any Jew who ever wore a shtreimel-- you know, the fur hat, which he did not-- and the kittel.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had his clothes made, made to order, and his hat made to order.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was a very beautiful man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was incredibly religious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I understand, or I understood those days that he was highly regarded for his Talmudic knowledge and Talmudic intelligence.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother wore a sheitel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my mother was a highly cultivated, socially conscious human being who was very-- enormously well-read.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And had it not been for the fact that she was a rabbi's daughter, she was-- her desire was to become a physician.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was very, very enlightened and intelligent and incredibly aware of the world.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And foretold us then-- god, so many decades ago-- that man will go to the moon.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
